# Luxanvoryx App File Structure

The app is organized into the following directory structure:

```
lib/
├── main.dart                 # App entry point
├── screens/                  # Main screens
│   ├── home_screen.dart      # Main screen with bottom navigation
│   ├── caffeine_tracker_screen.dart
│   ├── coupon_manager_screen.dart
│   └── color_generator_screen.dart
├── widgets/                  # Reusable UI components
│   ├── radial_progress.dart
│   ├── coupon_card.dart
│   ├── color_sphere.dart
│   └── ...
├── models/                   # Data models
│   ├── drink.dart
│   ├── coupon.dart
│   └── color_scheme.dart
├── repositories/             # Data access layer
│   ├── drink_repository.dart
│   ├── coupon_repository.dart
│   └── color_repository.dart
└── utils/                    # Helper functions and constants
    ├── constants.dart
    └── helpers.dart
```

Each feature (caffeine tracking, coupon management, color generation) should have its own dedicated files for screens, models, and repositories.
